storyInfo: Asked by Dur-nar to look after Bubble, Sideroca begins to spar with the young operator, only for her to slip away. Just as she reports this incident to Dur-nar, she suddenly comes to realize there is something more important she must do.

attributes.content: Hello? Can you hear me?
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Y-Yes.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Waagh—!

attributes.content: Uhh...

attributes.content: Okay.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Have fun with your training!

attributes.content: Wahhhh—!

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Sideroca looking after Bubble... I wonder how this will turn out.

Training Room No. 6.
You're a good runner, Forte lady.

Aghh... hah... hah...

Forte lady, I... I'm so exhausted...

Training Center Entrance.
So Bubble just disappeared after that?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Yes...

attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Please, punish me however you want!

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Haha...
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I'm very happy to hear that.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Yeah.

attributes.content: Uh—Hm?
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Oh, um... Well, about that.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: It's getting late, so why don't you head home and get some rest? I'll talk to the other instructors about that over the next couple of days. I should have some good news for you later.

attributes.content: We won't be as lucky next time.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: I'm certain we'll have a solution ready before this happens again.

attributes.content: How about Bubble? Any improvement on that end?

attributes.content: I looked at the camera footage already.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: You really should watch it yourself.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: My guess is that just hearing the name Sideroca is going to send her shivering to no end for a good while.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Did you just say my name, Instructor?

attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Oh, you're here too, Instructor Dobermann. Are you finished with your field op already?

attributes.content: Yeah... I was just looking at prospective sites around the landship.

attributes.content: That's wonderful to hear. Actually, I came back because I wanted to ask something. Would it be okay if I get started with the course tomorrow?
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: About that—
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: (Whispers) Think of something to dodge the question. You're good at that, aren't you?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: (Whispers) Dur-nar?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: (Whispers) I've actually talked to someone who knows Sideroca really well.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) She's surprised about Sideroca's current condition, but she did give me some constructive advice.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) She'll listen to me.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) Okay, I'm counting on you.
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Sideroca.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Yes!
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Here's the deal.

attributes.content: I was actually just discussing that with Instructor Dobermann.

attributes.content: We don't think more training will satisfy your needs.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) Hey, what's the big idea?!

attributes.content: (Whispers) Just trust me this once!

attributes.content: What do you mean...?

attributes.content: I know you sometimes work as the Doctor's bodyguard, and the Doctor slips away from you a lot.

attributes.content: That's all my fault. I'm so sorry!

attributes.content: That's why I need to—

attributes.content: You mean?

attributes.content: I'm sure you've noticed the Doctor hasn't been doing very well. Hardly ever getting enough sleep, and I've never seen anyone with worse eating habits. There's probably at least a tiny bit of chronic condition at work.

attributes.content: Rather than trying to improve your combat techniques, wouldn't you agree it's a much better idea to try to help the Doctor get better and healthier?

attributes.content: You should really think about what I just said. Good night, Sideroca.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: Good night... Instructor...
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: (Whispers) It's called being smart.
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) Don't just stand there. Let's go!
attributes.name: Dur-nar

attributes.content: (Whispers) At the very least, she's thinking about it. Let's get going!

attributes.content: She's right.

attributes.content: I thought all a bodyguard had to do was protect her employer.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: There is so much more that I can do, but the idea never even crossed my mind.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Oh...
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: Is that what the president meant?
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: I may not be very demanding with what I eat, but eating better will improve my quality of life.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: The president's coming all the way here to Rhodes Island, and I invited her to a meal at the cafeteria.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: I really shouldn't have.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: The Doctor probably thinks so too.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: The Doctor's just too shy to talk to me about it.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: I've made up my mind.
attributes.name: Sideroca

attributes.content: I will save the Doctor.
attributes.name: Sideroca
